prompt.en:
**Problem**
Implement the class hierarchy such that the code in main displays the expected output.

**Observations:**
- Extract words from the text received as an argument and put them into the sentence.
- Words are separated only by a single space.

**UML:**
Class hierarchy:
- Text (Abstract) with public method Afiseaza().
- Cuvant (inherits from Text) with private member 'txt: String' and public methods Afiseaza(), SetCuvant(cuvant: String), Cuvant(std: String).
- Propozitie (inherits from Text) with private member 'cuvinte[0..*]: Cuvant' and public methods Afiseaza(), AddCuvant(cuv: Cuvant), Propozitie(prop: String).
- Paragraf (inherits from Text) with private member 'texte[0..*]: Text' and public methods Afiseaza(), Add(txt: Text).

**main():**
```cpp
int main()
{
  Propozitie prop1("Ana are mere");
  Propozitie prop2("Ionel are cirese");
  Cuvant si("si");
  Cuvant mere("mere");
  Cuvant nl("\n");
  Cuvant tab("\t");
  Propozitie prop3("Vara se coc fructele");

  prop2.AddCuvant(si); prop2.AddCuvant(mere);

  Paragraf p;
  p.Add(&prop1);
  p.Add(&nl);
  p.Add(&tab);
  p.Add(&prop2);
  p.Add(&nl);
  p.Add(&prop3);
  p.Add(&nl);
  p.Afiseaza();
  return 0;
}
```

**Expected output:**
```
Ana are mere.
Ionel are cirese si mere.
Vara se coc fructele.
```

